<h4>Hint 1:</h4>
<p>
Don't implement your algorithm with the <i>if</i> conditions in the
same order as the problem description. 
</p>

<p>
If you do your solution will be wrong. It's easy to do; nothing saps
critical thinking skills like being nervous!
</p>

<p>
Also, do you remember what the lowest common multiple of two numbers
is?
</p>
